    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6 ">
            <h3 class="text-center">It's Simple</h3>
            <p>
                &nbsp;
            </p>
            <p>
                Click the REQUEST A NEW CAR button and select your ideal CAR from the drop-down menu. You can also call us on 0860 (277 423) if you prefer.
            </p>

            <p> Once we receive and verify your request, we activate the auction process by sending the new car request to dealers so that they can bid to give you the best price. </p>

            <p>
                Dealers have Your selected number of days to submit their best deals after which we close the auction and allocate a winning bid. If you accept the winning bid, we share your provided details with the dealer and the transaction is concluded between yourself and the dealer.
            </p>



        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h3 class="text-center">What Happens Next</h3>
            <p>
                &nbsp;
            </p>
            <p>
                Once you have entered your details and selected a new car, one of our call centre operators will contact you to confirm your details and thereafter activate the auction process
            </p>

            <p> Your vehicle request is then sent to the dealers who commence bidding and compete to offer you the best price. To keep you in the loop of the bidding, you will receive a link to follow the auction process and review incoming bids. </p>

            <p>
                We don’t share your information with any of the dealers during the auction period and will only provide the winning dealer with your information if you agree to proceed.
            </p>


        </div>
    </div>
    <hr>
